{"tid":2405023,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬斯克計劃讓新款特斯拉Roadster擁有[red]懸浮能力","createTime":"2021-02-12T05:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T09:56:35.000Z","uid":295230,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e20d83d8dca46924bc1ed48eccccb8c917073602","tid":2405023,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:29:20.000Z","msg":"痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>馬斯克計劃讓新款特斯拉Roadster擁有<span class=\"red\">懸浮能力</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n據外媒報導，埃隆&middot;馬斯克多年來一直表示，他希望提供一個火箭推進器包以提高第二代特斯拉跑車Roadster的速度。實際上，這款車的速度已經相當的快。但現在他表示，他正在考慮使用推進器使這款跑車能實現懸浮。據悉，這個想法則是馬斯克在最新一集Joe Rogan Experience節目中告訴主持人Joe Rogan的。<br />\n<br />\n英文來源︰<br />\n<strong>Elon Musk wants to make the Tesla Roadster hover -- yes, really</strong><br />\n<br />\nOn this week's installment of &quot;Did Elon Musk really just say that?&quot; we find him talking to podcaster (and isolation tank/psychedelics enthusiast) Joe Rogan about making the new Tesla Roadster hover.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">&quot;I want it to hover, and I was trying to figure out how to make this thing hover without, you know, killing people,&quot; Musk said in a recent episode of the Joe Rogan Experience, released Thursday. &quot;Maybe it can hover like a meter above the ground, or something like that. If you plummet, it'll blow out the suspension, but you're not gonna die.&quot;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2021/2/11/22278792/elon-musk-joe-rogan-tesla-roadster-spacex-hover-thrusters\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2021%2F2%2F11%2F22278792%2Felon-musk-joe-rogan-tesla-roadster-spacex-hover-thrusters&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=8027f077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2021/2/11/22278792/elon-musk-joe-rogan-tesla-roadster-spacex-hover-thrusters</a>"},{"pid":"dd62828c6ce8b35590e3ddaa6e93c446876fe594","tid":2405023,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:30:02.000Z","msg":"影片來源︰<br />\n<br />\n大概係1:00:00附近<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SJefd-ByybM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSJefd-ByybM&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=f4bbf85e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SJefd-ByybM</a>"},{"pid":"c02b662d7d52cf99c91b3f664f7ad82eba2597c9","tid":2405023,"uid":8662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:30:42.000Z","msg":"好撚科幻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b08ba83277991bd7104e4f277927ea8478dc2aa","tid":2405023,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:32:02.000Z","msg":"佢個地下隧道幾時通車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7c98f0d6f5f36a766e16fc6d02b07049cc60e6","tid":2405023,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b08ba83277991bd7104e4f277927ea8478dc2aa","tid":2405023,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:32:02.000Z","msg":"佢個地下隧道幾時通車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:32:42.000Z","msg":"LAS VEGAS隧道前星期已完工"},{"pid":"a24ea0f554c56f8a5c10415891fff1ced74b0765","tid":2405023,"uid":230594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:33:08.000Z","msg":"May the Force be with you<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bea566e1a794b29